---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Inspired Mile â€” how we handle your data and protect your privacy.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm mb-12">Last updated: February 15, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-brand-slate text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">Overview</h2>
          <p>
            Inspired Mile (<a href="https://inspiredmile.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">inspiredmile.com</a>) is operated by Voyage Tracable, LLC. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect (almost none) and how we handle it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-3"><strong class="text-white">We do not collect any personal data.</strong> Specifically:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li>No cookies are set or read</li>
            <li>No analytics or tracking scripts are used</li>
            <li>No user accounts or login systems exist</li>
            <li>No forms collect personal information</li>
            <li>No advertising networks are present</li>
            <li>No third-party scripts are loaded</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">AI Assistant</h2>
          <p>
            This site includes an AI assistant that runs <strong class="text-white">entirely in your browser</strong> using WebLLM technology. The AI model is downloaded to your device and all processing happens locally. No conversations, prompts, or responses are sent to any server. Your interactions with the AI assistant are completely private.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">Fonts &amp; Assets</h2>
          <p>
            All fonts and assets are self-hosted on our servers. No requests are made to Google Fonts, CDNs, or any other third-party services. This means your IP address is never shared with external font or asset providers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">Server Logs</h2>
          <p>
            Our web server may automatically log standard access information (IP address, page requested, timestamp, browser type) as part of normal server operation. These logs are used solely for security monitoring and are not shared with any third party. They are retained for no more than 30 days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">External Links</h2>
          <p>
            This site may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any external site you visit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">
            Under regulations including the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li>Know what personal data we collect (we collect none)</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your personal data (there is none to delete)</li>
            <li>Opt out of the sale of your personal data (we do not sell any data)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Since we do not collect, store, or process any personal data, these rights are satisfied by default.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            This site does not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13 (COPPA) or 16 (GDPR). Since we collect no personal data from any visitor, this requirement is met by default.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            If we make changes to this privacy policy, we will update the &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date at the top of this page. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:david@davidjcharlot.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">david@davidjcharlot.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
